flowchart TB
  DC[Datacenter] --> NET[Client/Backup/Management Network]
  DC --> RACK[Exadata Rack]
  RACK --> DB[Database Servers: GI ASM DB]
  RACK --> CELL[Storage Cells: Exadata System Software]
  DB <--> INT[Internal RDMA Network: IB or RoCE]
  CELL <--> INT
  CELL --> ASM[ASM Diskgroups DATA RECO DBFS]
  DB --> MON[Enterprise Manager / AHF / Exachk]
